snippet.title: GOD EATER 3 - Update Version 1.30 Story Trailer | PS4, Steam
snippet.description:
What happens after the main story ends in GOD EATER 3? Find out in this FREE #GODEATER3 update which also features new allies and new Aragami! 

Patch 1.30 "Another Devil" has been released and is available now! Check out the full patch notes here: https://bandainamcoent.com/news/patch-notes-130-and-131-released

#GODEATER #BandaiNamco
